et list, huh~... We should make it one with a lot of impact! One that'll set the atmosphere of the room in an instant!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event169-02-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Wouldn't that depend on whatever atmosphere the band playing before us sets?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event169-02-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"That's a good point... I think the band before us plays a lot of pretty low-key songs~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event169-02-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"Then that means our first song's gotta have some oomph!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event169-02-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"That's what you always say.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"pui01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event169-02-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"But you wanna grab the crowd's attention from the very beginning, don't you? Show 'em all, y'know... \"This is the Afterglow of the here and now!\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event169-02-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"Hm... In that case, then I guess... \"SENSENFUKOKU?\"","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event169-02-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":8}],"windowDisplayName":"Himari","body":"That'd work, but... what about a new song? I've been thinking it's about time.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":8,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":8,"voiceId":"event169-02-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Hii-chan, nice idea~. That gets one Moca-chan vote~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event169-02-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"I was actually thinking about a new song yesterday.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event169-02-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"Moca","body":"Oooh~, that's the Ran I know~. You work fast~.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"event169-02-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"Problem is, I can't come up with anything concrete. That's why I want to hear what kind of song you all want to make.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event169-02-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":10}],"windowDisplayName":"Tsugumi","body":"The last song we made was a summer song, right?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":10,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":10,"voiceId":"event169-02-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"If that's the case, then-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":9,"motionName":"simizimi01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":9,"voiceId":"event169-02-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":6}],"windowDisplayName":"Ran","body":"I'll say it now, \"oomph\" is banned. So is \"deep,\" Moca.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":6,"motionName":"nnf02","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":6,"voiceId":"event169-02-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":9}],"windowDisplayName":"Tomoe","body":"Ugh... You really gonna go there~? It's so easy to understand though. Y'know, it's just... Oomph.","tention":0,"lipSyncM